channel.title: Changing time on wcing trees
channel.description: On my server the trees are funny you will be wcing the normal tree at lvl 1 and then at lvl 99 you will be wcing and it will be 10 times faster. Is there any way to change the timing of the trees? Like because it's pissing the people that play my server off because the magic tree takes 32 seconds to wc lol.
